Package de.rwth.swc.coffee4j.junit.engine.annotation.parameter

Class ParameterValueLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.swc.coffee4j.junit.engine.annotation.parameter.ParameterValueLoader
  • public class ParameterValueLoader
extends Object
    Loads the object which is supposed to injected for a method parameter for a given ParameterContext.

    Assumes that there is exactly one ParameterValueSource (meta-)annotation present on the parameter which may be initialized with a AnnotationConsumerInitializer.
